Unified Admin Settings System

A completely redesigned settings system that provides a consistent, modern experience across all admin settings pages:

    â€¢ Unified Settings Component: All extension settings pages now share a common, beautifully designed interface


    â€¢ Tab-Based Organization: Settings are organized into logical tabs with smooth animations and visual indicators


    â€¢ Field Type Support: Support for switches, text inputs, numbers, ranges, URLs, selects, file uploads, and custom components


    â€¢ Quick Stats Badges: Each tab shows at-a-glance counts of toggles, selects, and other field types


    â€¢ Conditional Fields: Settings can show/hide based on other setting values


    â€¢ Real-Time Validation: Instant feedback on setting changes with unsaved changes tracking


    â€¢ Responsive Design: Fully responsive layout that works on all screen sizes

