All extension landing pages now feature the main site footer (SiteFooter) for better navigation:

    â€¢ Consistent Footer: Landing pages for all extensions (staking, affiliate, copy-trading, etc.) show the full site footer


    â€¢ Subpage Footer: Non-landing pages within extensions show the standard dashboard footer


    â€¢ Reusable Wrapper: New ExtensionLayoutWrapper component handles footer logic based on current path


    â€¢ Custom Subpage Footers: Extensions can optionally provide their own custom footer for subpages (e.g., NFT's minimal footer)

