Bug Fixes

Homepage Stability

    â€¢ Fixed Scroll Animation Error: Resolved "Target ref is defined but not hydrated" error that occurred when navigating to the homepage


    â€¢ Mobile App Section Fix: Fixed the same hydration issue in the mobile app section's parallax animations


    â€¢ Smoother Transitions: Page transitions no longer cause animation-related errors

Notification Sound Glitch

    â€¢ Fixed Audio Glitch on Page Load: Notification sound no longer makes a brief glitch sound when pages load


    â€¢ Lazy Audio Loading: Sound files are now loaded only after user interaction, preventing autoplay issues


    â€¢ Silent Unlock: Audio system unlocks silently without playing any audible sound


    â€¢ Better Browser Compatibility: Improved handling for iOS Safari and other restrictive browsers

Settings Quick Stats

    â€¢ Fixed Empty Badges: Settings tabs no longer show "0 toggles" or "0 selects" badges when there are no fields of that type


    â€¢ Conditional Display: Badges only appear when there are actual fields to count

Rich Text Editor

    â€¢ Simplified Editor Component: Streamlined the editor component for better performance


    â€¢ Removed Quill Dependency: Editor now uses a lighter-weight implementation

Notification Page

    â€¢ Filter Spacing: Fixed "1Active filter" text to properly show space between count and word

